---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="ostk privacy policy. The software collects nothing. The website uses Plausible for aggregate page views only. No cookies, no tracking.">
  <main id="main-content" class="pt-16 pb-12 px-4 md:px-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="py-12">
      <div class="section-label mb-4">LEGAL // PRIVACY</div>
      <h1 class="serif-text text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-outline mb-12">
        Effective: 2026-03-11 · <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@ostk.ai</a>
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">Summary</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The software collects nothing. It runs locally on your machine — no telemetry, no phone-home. The website uses Plausible Analytics for aggregate page view counts only: no cookies, no personal data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">The Software</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary mb-4">ostk runs entirely on your local machine. It does not:</p>
        <ul class="font-body text-xs text-secondary space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Send data to any server</li>
          <li>Collect usage statistics</li>
          <li>Phone home for license checks</li>
          <li>Upload files, logs, or audit trails</li>
          <li>Require network access for any core functionality</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary mt-4">
          All state lives in your filesystem under <code class="text-primary">.ostk/</code> in your repository. You own it. You can read it. You can delete it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">The Website (ostk.ai)</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary mb-4">
          ostk uses Plausible Analytics — a privacy-first analytics tool with no cookies, no cross-site tracking, and full GDPR/CCPA compliance.
        </p>
        <ul class="font-body text-xs text-secondary space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Does not use cookies</li>
          <li>Does not track individual visitors</li>
          <li>Does not collect personal information</li>
          <li>Records aggregate page view counts and outbound link clicks only</li>
          <li>Serves static content only</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">Third Parties</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          The website uses <a href="https://plausible.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">Plausible Analytics</a>, which processes only aggregate, anonymous page view data. No personal data is shared. The software shares no data with any third party.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
        Questions: <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@ostk.ai</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
